name: Arnold Lowrey Watercolour Palette
description:
A watercolour palette designed by Arnold Lowrey
It has a flat mixing area with open ended wells designed to have full control of the water.
Using the included sponge it ensures that the tube paints stay dry by inserting the sponge with the lid on between painting sessions.


£16 including postage
